text: Kivisaar in 2011 Alari Kivisaar (born 16 January 1967 in Tartu) is an Estonian television personality and nature photographer, best known as the host of the game show Võta või jäta. ==References== Category:Estonian television personalities Category:Living people Category:1967 births Category:Estonian game show hosts Category:Estonian photographers Category:People from Tartu
